00:19:03,271 --> 00:19:16,326
So this business of morality is understood to be of prime importance to understand this business of ethics and morality.

243
00:19:17,406 --> 00:19:22,231
Some of you may know that there are four stages to liberation.

244
00:19:22,599 --> 00:19:25,063
what we call the stream entrant.

245
00:19:25,663 --> 00:19:29,086
And that's somebody who's broken through this wrong view of self.

246
00:19:29,208 --> 00:19:32,832
It's only a lightning understanding of it.

247
00:19:32,892 --> 00:19:34,773
The sense of self is still very strong.

248
00:19:35,674 --> 00:19:46,326
And then the second level is when somebody has such an insight that their greed and hatred is much undermined.

249
00:19:48,028 --> 00:19:49,029
And in the third level,

250
00:19:49,346 --> 00:19:53,192
the greed and hatred aversion is completely gone.

251
00:19:53,852 --> 00:20:00,621
And that simply means that the person is no longer attracted to this level of existence.

252
00:20:00,641 --> 00:20:02,303
But there are still five things to go.

253
00:20:02,323 --> 00:20:06,307
Restlessness, well, the main one is conceit.

254
00:20:07,048 --> 00:20:10,873
And that includes the sense of I am.

255
00:20:10,893 --> 00:20:13,296
Now,

256
00:20:13,596 --> 00:20:25,288
Such is the importance of understanding or accepting the law of karma, the law of consequence, that if you do something harmful, something harmful will arise.

257
00:20:25,388 --> 00:20:27,971
If you do something wholesome, something wholesome will arise.

258
00:20:30,953 --> 00:20:37,740
Somebody who actually takes that on is known as a chula sotapanna, so a lesser stream entrant.

259
00:20:37,941 --> 00:20:41,223
That's how important the commentaries put to it.

260
00:20:41,344 --> 00:20:43,266
I don't think it's in the scriptures themselves.

261
00:20:43,684 --> 00:20:44,465
It's the beginning.

262
00:20:44,747 --> 00:20:45,448
It's the beginning.

263
00:20:45,488 --> 00:20:47,009
Because why is that?

264
00:20:47,049 --> 00:20:53,699
Because our ethics, our morality is an expression of this original delusion.

265
00:20:54,319 --> 00:20:58,787
